Package com.example.tundra_snow_app.Models

Class Facilities

java.lang.Object
com.example.tundra_snow_app.Models.Facilities
public class Facilities extends Object
Represents a facility where an event can occur. It encapsulates details such as a unique facility ID, the name of the facility, and its location.
